@{LINDENT 4}
@{PAR}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}Flip@{UB}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Perform one or more flip operations on a portable anymap.@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}Reads a portable anymap as input. Performs one or more flip operations,
in the order specified, and writes out a portable anymap.@{LINE}
